Package ru.tinkoff.qa.neptune.core.api.dependency.injection

Interface DependencyInjector

public interface DependencyInjector
It is designed for the filling of not static and not final fields of objects. It is recommended to implement by classes which have no declared constructor/constructor without parameters.
